---
description: Spec generation rules
alwaysApply: false
globs:
  - "spec/**"
  - "scripts/build_mvp.py"
  - "scripts/tighten_results_from_examples.py"
---

When editing specs or generators:
- Maintain split: projection vs transport.
- Projection may use virtual paths; transport must remain executable.
- Preserve `x-sweb-upstream-path` and `x-sweb-upstream-method`.
- After changes run build + tighten + validate.
